---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Network configuration and maintenance, installation of services and servers</h2>
		<p>with a strong experiense in network configuration and maintenance, as well as a proven ability in installing services and servers, I am capable of effectively managing an IT network. My experience allows me to apply key concepts to ensure optimal performence, enhanced security, and continuous service availability.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="monitoring" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Monitoring and security system</h2>
		<p>I am very passionate about security system and network monitoring because I have had a lot of experience working with various tools such as Nagios, EyesOfNetwork,PRTG, Cacti, PFSense and snort. </p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="strategy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>frond-end developer</h2>
		<p>I have good skills in programming languages and technologies such as: HTML,CSS,Javascript,bootstrap. I am curious and keep abreast of the latest trends and developments. in addition to my technical skills, I am able to solve problems, I have an understanding of user experience.</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
